info.title: Spokane Economic Dashboard
info.description: API Endpoints for interactions between the MongoDB cluster and the Census Bureau API

tags.name: Auth
tags.description: Authorized endpoints for logging into the admin page, as well as registering a new user or changing their password

get.summary: Render 'The Button' page for the user
Render the manual input indicator update page for the user
Render the admin page for the user
Render the login page for the user

post.summary: Submit a username and password to be verified by the application
post.description: Endpoint interacts with MongoDb to retrieve a user and it's stored password and match it to the inputted values. If there is a match, redirect the user to the

302.description: Successful login. Redirect to admin page

403.description: Bad login. Reload login page and try again

get.summary: Render the register page for the user

post.summary: Register new authorized email to access the admin page
post.description: Endpoint checks if the user's email is valid, then it saves the user's username and redirects them to the admin page

302.description: Successfully registered user. Redirect to admin page

get.summary: Render the change password page for the user

post.summary: Submit the user's email to the change password service
post.description: Checks if the user is a registered user of the application, then it emails the user a pin code and redirects them to the pin verification page

get.summary: Render the verify pin page for the user

200.description: Success. Render the verify pin page

post.summary: Submit a pin and new password.
post.description: The endpoint verifies that the submitted pin matches the pin sent to the user and that it was submitted in the proper amount of time. Then it will update the requesting user's password with the new value

302.description: Successfully verified pin and changed password. Redirect to admin page

401.description: Failed to verify pin. Redirect to change password page
